title: Statement by the Press Secretary on H.J. Res. 131 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
December 13, 2014

 



Statement by the Press Secretary on H.J. Res. 131




On Saturday, December 13, 2014, the President signed into law:
H.J. Res. 131, which provides fiscal year 2015 appropriations for projects and activities of the Federal Government through Wednesday, December 17, 2014
